# All @sleepingasteroid/bluehop-* packages are published to the public npm registry (the default),
# so no scope/registry override is needed here.
#
# Auth is NOT committed. Publishing requires an npm token:
#   - CI: actions/setup-node with registry-url injects NODE_AUTH_TOKEN (see release.yml), or
#   - locally: run `npm login`, or add to your ~/.npmrc:
#       //registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=YOUR_NPM_TOKEN
